Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜組裝起來的 不要弄壞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 不要鬆手 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 "規則"是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(328,355)}{\fs20}Regulation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似於決定機器能否參賽的一種標準吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差距太大的話就稱不上比賽了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego看上去像是市販的量產型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面卻有岡倉老師裝的優化組件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(462,355)}{\fs20}Custom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架構跟外形就已經違規了 沒法讓它出賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 BALON和Fuego一樣是特努強機動公司生產的新型號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作系統也是一樣的 小琳的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真服了妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始不就告訴妳要當心點的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 別鬧了 快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Fuego的話就很不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力練習的獎賞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過這半個月的特訓 妳騎得不錯了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算參賽也沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是比賽了 我會和妳決個分曉出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定出任GGP治安維持部\N隊司令官的羅曼洛夫·卡連巴古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已抵達橫田基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周預定舉行的就任儀式上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以首相為首的內閣官僚們將出席…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:58.73,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:58.73,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:03.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:03.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:14.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:14.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:21.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:21.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:08.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
